        <item>
            <title>Version 1.6.1</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 23:51:40 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>8</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.6.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Bugfix — HUD invisible after several dictations</strong>. The recording HUD could get stuck invisible if you re-pressed the hotkey while the previous fade-out animation was still running. Dictation kept working but the on-screen indicator stopped appearing. Fixed by making the show animation supersede any in-flight fade-out.</li>
                    <li><strong>Slightly longer blur in / blur out</strong> on the HUD (0.40s in, 0.32s out, up from 0.22s / 0.18s) so the transitions feel less abrupt at both ends of a dictation.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            <enclosure
                url="https://github.com/krahim786/whisperly/releases/download/v1.6.1/Whisperly-local.dmg"
                sparkle:edSignature="4WKWnH8M0BTSwvgHuMrf6lwd4PQEfvcuc3vcORH8Z/1jiZe6QPnWGyVOXowv58WXQERajaMktPZwW38bN5ccBw=="
                length="6484429"
                type="application/octet-stream"
            />
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Version 1.6</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 15:29:25 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>7</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.6</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Action menu — Shift can be added mid-press</strong> — if you hold Right Option first and add Shift a beat later, the action menu now arms correctly. Previously the modifier was sampled only at press-time, so a slightly slow Shift was missed. Once armed, the HUD subtitle updates live to "Action menu" for visual confirmation.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            <enclosure
                url="https://github.com/krahim786/whisperly/releases/download/v1.6/Whisperly-local.dmg"
