            />
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Version 1.5</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 15:19:52 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>6</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.5</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Action menu</strong> — hold Right Option + Shift while dictating, then pick from a 4-button menu above the HUD: Grammar, Personal, Formal, or Shorter. Press Esc anywhere to cancel. Plain Right Option still pastes cleaned text immediately.</li>
                    <li><strong>HUD blur-in / blur-out</strong> — the recording HUD now blurs in when you press the hotkey and blurs out after pasting, so it's less abrupt at both ends of a dictation.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            <enclosure
                url="https://github.com/krahim786/whisperly/releases/download/v1.5/Whisperly-local.dmg"
