        <item>
            <title>Version 1.4</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 11:59:30 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>5</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.4</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>HUD position</strong> — the recording HUD now appears bottom-center of the active screen instead of bottom-right, so it stays out of the way of right-edge UI like sidebars and gets bothered less by Dock-on-the-right setups.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
