            <sparkle:version>4</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.3</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Permission diagnostics</strong> — when macOS resets Whisperly's Accessibility permission after an update, the menu bar now shows a banner with a one-click button to open System Settings instead of failing silently. A first-paste alert also fires once per session if the grant is missing.</li>
                </ul>
