            <pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 19:09:51 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>3</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Offline mode</strong> — when Groq is unreachable (no internet, API error, rate limit), Whisperly falls back to on-device speech recognition so you can keep dictating without a round-trip</li>
