        <item>
            <title>Version 1.1</title>
            <pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 14:00:03 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>2</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Translation</strong> — speak in any of 19 languages and Whisperly pastes the translation, with auto-detect or pinned source language</li>
                    <li><strong>Grammar correction</strong> — new "Writing assistance" setting fixes article use, verb tenses, prepositions, and L2 phrasing while preserving voice</li>
                    <li><strong>Live transcript preview</strong> — see what you're saying as you speak, via on-device speech recognition; Whisper still does the canonical pass</li>
                    <li><strong>Audio level meter</strong> — bars are alive from the moment you press the hotkey, with subtle ambient response and proper sensitivity curve</li>
                    <li><strong>Auto-updates</strong> — future versions will install automatically (this is the first release with Sparkle wired up)</li>
                    <li>Bundled-key family-share path, Urdu added, dictation-mode fixes</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            <enclosure
                url="https://github.com/krahim786/whisperly/releases/download/v1.1/Whisperly-local.dmg"
                sparkle:edSignature="LKT6Nz+Kvu61OY400e/hxkyCB01a9HqULFHHZi89CxykddKh3bcTkJvR7mktU+jaL63wXOb1TEkGwycI+1Q2Dw=="
